# Whitelist: include only what the deploy Dockerfile needs. The repo is
# enormous (1900 .cc files, contrib/, dat/, .venv/, intermediate build
# artifacts, etc.); shipping all of it as build context would bloat the
# upload to fly.io's remote builder for no reason.
**

!deploy/Dockerfile
!deploy/Caddyfile

